there is a lag between when the build report is published and when the web site is updated. There is also a lag introduced by the content delivery network -- the landing pages are cached at potentially many locations (your computer, your institution, the AWS cloudfront node). The lag can accumulate to several hours.

The most reliable source of information is the build report.

Martin

